text: Rolf Yelseth (25 February 1914 - 1968) was a South African gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:1968 deaths Category:South African male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of South Africa Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Durban
